From here?

00:57:09.260 --> 00:57:10.560
&gt;&gt; Yes.

00:57:10.560 --> 00:57:11.940
&gt;&gt; Let me try and slide-- wah-la.

00:57:11.940 --> 00:57:17.430 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Yes, I mean this is actually my
