00:57:29.810 --> 00:57:32.680
And really culminating
the happy resolution

00:57:32.680 --> 00:57:38.480 position:56%
of the Azerbaijan Crisis was
president Truman's formal invitation

00:57:38.480 --> 00:57:41.850 position:56%
extended to the youthful
[inaudible] Shah [inaudible] of Iran

00:57:41.850 --> 00:57:46.090
to visit the USA in 1949.

00:57:46.090 --> 00:57:51.780
His very first trip
