00:57:51.780 --> 00:57:56.620
By some happy chance, the
son of counsel retained

00:57:56.620 --> 00:58:03.710 position:56%
by the Iranian delegation to advice
them in conducting this crucial case

00:58:03.710 --> 00:58:09.190
against the Soviet Union was
the father of David Leland,

00:58:09.190 --> 00:58:11.410
who is sitting here
in the front row.

00:58:11.410 --> 00:58:14.420
And I'm so happy that
he's been able to be here.

00:58:14.420 --> 00:58:19.880
John Leland was a very
distinguished international lawyer

00:58:19.880 --> 00:58:22.730
who might have become
Secretary of State expect

00:58:22.730 --> 00:58:26.710
that he was a bit brusque
to his critics.

00:58:26.710 --> 00:58:29.020
And so that never happened.

00:58:29.020 --> 00:58:33.660
But he was a great family
friend as his children were.

00:58:33.660 --> 00:58:35.530
Thank you very much
for your attention.

00:58:35.530 --> 00:58:44.640
